# Silicon Valley Trail — Environment Variables
#
# GOOD NEWS: This game currently requires NO API keys!
# Open-Meteo (the weather API) is completely free and keyless.
#
# If you extend the game to use OpenWeatherMap, Hacker News, or other APIs
# that require keys, add them here and load them in your Java code with:
#   System.getenv("YOUR_KEY_NAME")
#
# IMPORTANT: NEVER commit actual API keys to GitHub.
# This .env.example file shows what keys exist (with no real values).
# The real .env file should be listed in .gitignore.

# Example (not currently used):
# OPENWEATHER_API_KEY=your_key_here
